    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm parting ways with my pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total beauty. This car has been babied since day one\u2014always garaged and kept in absolutely pristine condition. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
