    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in truly pristine condition. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I love this car to bits, but it's time for a new home. If you're looking for something that's been treated with total love and looks brand new, this is the one! Swing by, have a look, and let's chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
