    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, maintained to a museum-grade standard. This specimen features the high-revving F22C1 longitudinal inline-four, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The rigid X-bone frame and double-wishbone suspension remain factory-spec, exhibiting zero bushing degradation or chassis fatigue. Every mechanical component, from the VTEC solenoid engagement to the synchro mesh, operates with surgical precision. This is a collector-grade example with pristine undercarriage integrity and a flawless factory finish.",
